meta.name: Wheel of Fortune
meta.description: Contestants guess hidden phrases by guessing letters one at a time. Contestants win money or prizes, as determined by a spin of the wheel, for each correct consonant they guess. But they have to pay to see what vowels are in a puzzle. The contestant that has amassed the most winnings at the end of a game goes on to play the bonus round, in which the player can win even more -- prizes frequently seen in the bonus round include automobiles, vacations and more cash.

videos.title: Episode 48
videos.overview: Hosted by Pat Sajak, this game show features 3 contestants who try to solve a puzzle by guessing letters in a word or phrase. Vanna White is the letter-turner.
